   <body>
      <section name="What are property filters?">
         <p>Formally they are optional sufixes of the property name. But it is easier to
            understand what they are and why they are useful with an example.</p>
         <p>
            ...
         </p>
         <source>
            skin:teacher=blue
            skin:student.secundary=green
            skin:student=yellow
            skin=grey
         </source>
         <p>
            ...
         </p>
         <source>
            getProperties().getString("skin", Filter.by(userType, userSubtype));
         </source>
      </section>
   </body>
